reviewText: My son loves cars, trucks, motorcycles and all, but this movie was a big dissapointment.  It's a cheesy film that dosen't hold the intrest of our child.  I gave it away, thank god is wasn't that exspensive.
My son who is 4 LOVES this DVD. He LOVES the Cars video. It is one of his favorites!!

My 2 year old LOVES this DVD!!!  I have to order a new one because he will bring it to me and say "I wanna watch cars".  So now we have scratches on it and it skips.  My 7 and 9 year old think it is interesting as well. They will sit and watch the whole thing with their brother.  I do agree that the actors are a little cheezy, but as long as the kids like it I am ok with that.
